Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.17,0:06:14.22,Main,Ryuuma,0,0,0,,Did his wound just ignite?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.00,0:06:24.11,Main,Ryuuma,0,0,0,,I lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.86,0:06:33.52,Main,Ryuuma,0,0,0,,Shuusui, the famous sword that once served a legendary samurai.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.86,0:06:33.52,Note,Ryuuma,0,0,0,,Shuusui: Clear Autumn Water
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.52,0:06:39.21,Main,Ryuuma,0,0,0,,Surely this sword will be satisfied under your command.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.81,0:06:43.71,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,Did that samurai just say something?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.00,0:06:45.01,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,So that means...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.01,0:06:47.18,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,w-what exactly?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.18,0:06:48.99,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,It means...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.99,0:06:51.68,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,that the match is over!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.68,0:06:54.62,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,I've never seen a battle like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.26,0:06:57.40,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,That samurai...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.40,0:07:02.27,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,never fought against me seriously!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.27,0:07:05.75,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,And some fight that was.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.62,0:07:17.03,Main,Ryuuma,0,0,0,,I feel sorry for...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.03,0:07:21.50,Main,Ryuuma,0,0,0,,giving this samurai body a complete defeat...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.50,0:07:24.24,Main,Zoro,0,0,0,,Having the feeling of shame is enough...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.24,0:07:27.56,Main,Zoro,0,0,0,,That's what makes a true swordsman in both body and soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.56,0:07:30.26,Main,Zoro,0,0,0,,I wish I could've met you when you were alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.85,0:07:38.68,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,T-This is...!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.68,0:07:39.87,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,It's back!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.87,0:07:44.02,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,After five long years, my shadow is finally back!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.02,0:07:46.43,Main,Zoro,0,0,0,,I'll be taking the sword, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.43,0:07:49.34,Main,Zoro,0,0,0,,let's pretend this duel never happened,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.34,0:07:51.70,Main,Zoro,0,0,0,,samurai of Wano Country.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.90,0:08:01.66,Main,Hogback,0,0,0,,Well? How does it feel\Nto get captured by your own friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.40,0:08:06.13,Main,Jigoro,0,0,0,,You failed to feed me salt with that weird ability!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.82,0:08:07.84,Thoughts,Robin,0,0,0,,He's strong...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.49,0:08:12.46,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,Damn! I never thought Sanji would kick Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.46,0:08:14.82,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,This creature is no longer Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.82,0:08:17.42,Main,Dog-Penguin,0,0,0,,Who's this Sanji?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.42,0:08:19.26,Main,Dog-Penguin,0,0,0,,I'll kill you, damn bastard.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.76,0:08:26.52,Main,Hogback,0,0,0,,Unfortunately for you, they no longer have memories of being your friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.52,0:08:30.95,Main,Hogback,0,0,0,,Fresh zombies may have\Nremains of their former selves,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.95,0:08:34.70,Main,Hogback,0,0,0,,but now that the body and shadow have merged completely...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.70,0:08:37.03,Main,Hogback,0,0,0,,their humanity is gone for good.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.03,0:08:40.51,Main,Hogback,0,0,0,,They're my loyal zombies now!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.51,0:08:44.22,Main,Hogback,0,0,0,,And for a zombie, orders are absolute!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.72,0:08:51.02,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,I'm almost glad that you've fallen this low, Hogback!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.67,0:08:58.87,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,You once saved numerous human lives,\Nthat's why I deeply admired you as a doctor,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.87,0:09:01.52,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,even your zombie research.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.52,0:09:02.72,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,Death...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.72,0:09:04.69,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,it comes without warning...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.13,0:09:11.89,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,Because of this, many things are left unsaid between those dead and those left behind...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.89,0:09:13.60,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,Not for many years...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.60,0:09:15.49,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,just a few minutes would be enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.49,0:09:19.55,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,If there was a way to bring back the dead for even a brief moment...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.55,0:09:23.49,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,even if it was an evil and heretical practice...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.20,0:09:27.04,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,it would be hugely appreciated by those who were brought back!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.49,0:09:35.34,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,That's why, when you spoke of raising the dead, I thought your words were...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.99,0:09:38.14,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,worthy of a true doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.87,0:09:44.68,Main,Hogback,0,0,0,,Fool! Why would I do that for strangers?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.77,0:09:49.69,Main,Hogback,0,0,0,,They requested my aid for the same reason you admired me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.00,0:09:53.00,Main,Hogback,0,0,0,,It was because I was a genius!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.70,0:09:56.19,Main,Hogback,0,0,0,,It was all about the money!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.19,0:10:01.43,Main,Hogback,0,0,0,,I didn't want to help all those patients who kept coming incessantly from all over the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.16,0:10:03.45,Main,Hogback,0,0,0,,"Please help my father!"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.45,0:10:04.77,Main,Hogback,0,0,0,,"Save my child!"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.77,0:10:06.32,Main,Hogback,0,0,0,,"Help my boyfriend!"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.32,0:10:09.37,Main,Hogback,0,0,0,,What a huge annoyance!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.90,0:10:11.34,Main,Hogback,0,0,0,,So troublesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.27,0:10:16.38,Main,Hogback,0,0,0,,I had to pay for the incompetence of all those pathetic doctors who couldn't even save a life.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.22,0:10:19.93,Main,Hogback,0,0,0,,Can you comprehend the trouble of being such a genius?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.70,0:10:23.78,Main,Hogback,0,0,0,,Whether you respect me or not is up to you,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.78,0:10:26.15,Main,Hogback,0,0,0,,but the mere fact that I disappointed you is ridiculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.15,0:10:30.17,Main,Hogback,0,0,0,,If you can't stand me as a doctor because of your absurd ideals...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.42,0:10:33.47,Main,Hogback,0,0,0,,Then you're deceiving yourself, stupid reindeer!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.47,0:10:36.71,Main,Hogback,0,0,0,,You want to tell me what a doctor should be?!{edited for clarity - Sky}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.71,0:10:38.97,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,I don't intend to tell you anything!{Retranslated to match previous line - Sky}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.97,0:10:41.95,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,I don't think of you as a doctor anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.44,0:10:45.62,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,The same goes for those zombies!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.15,0:10:48.91,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,They're just empty shells moving to your will!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.91,0:10:50.62,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,They're not alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.15,0:10:53.00,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,Don't play with life!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.56,0:10:56.72,Main,Hogback,0,0,0,,What a cruel statement.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.72,0:11:00.45,Main,Hogback,0,0,0,,You deny their livelihood despite seeing them move before your very eyes?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.59,0:11:05.06,Main,Hogback,0,0,0,,Granting a new life to the dead is a true miracle!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.18,0:11:08.93,Main,Hogback,0,0,0,,How can you possibly deny the existence of this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.22,0:11:10.09,Main,Hogback,0,0,0,,Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.40,0:11:20.40,Main,Hogback,0,0,0,,Now then, lick the floor, Cindry.{the first , seems appropriate here, should probably leave it}{added "then" to give it proper pacing in english - Sky}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.40,0:11:23.70,Main,Hogback,0,0,0,,Yes, Hogback-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.63,0:11:32.10,Main,Hogback,0,0,0,,You saw that room, didn't you, Dr. Chopper?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.44,0:11:35.94,Main,Hogback,0,0,0,,That's my room.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.75,0:11:41.55,Main,Hogback,0,0,0,,All those were pictures of the stage actress Victoria Cindry, back when she was alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.55,0:11:45.26,Main,Hogback,0,0,0,,I completely fell in love with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.26,0:11:50.67,Main,Hogback,0,0,0,,Not only me, but men from the entire country, fell for such beauty.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.02,0:11:55.77,Flashbacks,Cindry,0,0,0,,It's fixed now, Doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.77,0:12:00.09,Flashbacks,Hogback,0,0,0,,S-Sorry, I didn't mean to disturb my patient just to get my buttons sewn!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.00,0:12:03.17,Flashbacks,Cindry,0,0,0,,It's no problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.83,0:12:10.13,Main,Hogback,0,0,0,,A very popular yet unpretentious person...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.13,0:12:11.62,Main,Hogback,0,0,0,,devoted to her family,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.33,0:12:20.21,Main,Hogback,0,0,0,,She was kind to everyone... truly a wonderful woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.21,0:12:22.22,Main,Hogback,0,0,0,,but she...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.18,0:12:37.00,Main,Hogback,0,0,0,,rejected my proposal, the proposal of a doctor who had everything...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.00,0:12:39.19,Main,Hogback,0,0,0,,All because of that accursed fianc√© of hers...!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.19,0:12:40.48,Main,Hogback,0,0,0,,And then...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.48,0:12:44.61,Main,Hogback,0,0,0,,Unbelievable news reached my ears...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.04,0:12:47.63,Main,Hogback,0,0,0,,Cindry... died in an accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.51,0:12:52.54,Main,Hogback,0,0,0,,My pain was indescribable...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.54,0:12:55.36,Main,Hogback,0,0,0,,I abandoned my work...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.36,0:12:59.63,Main,Hogback,0,0,0,,It was then that a huge man appeared before me...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.04,0:13:03.21,Main,Hogback,0,0,0,,My master, Gekko Moriah!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.03,0:13:07.41,Flashbacks,Hogback,0,0,0,,Dr. Hogback, lend me your power!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.55,0:13:18.06,Main,Hogback,0,0,0,,So we agreed that, in exchange for resurrecting Cindry with his miraculous ability, I would stay on this ship.{maybe we should split this into 3 parts? to avoid the sceene bleeding? -punkid}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.80,0:13:20.94,Main,Hogback,0,0,0,,I stole her body...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.24,0:13:25.40,Main,Hogback,0,0,0,,and by doing so, I easily gained control over the actress Cindry!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.80,0:13:29.22,Main,Hogback,0,0,0,,Cindry-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.08,0:13:34.44,Main,Cindry,0,0,0,,It would be best if all the plates disappear...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.90,0:13:40.25,Main,Hogback,0,0,0,,I didn't care about who the woman was inside her body...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.25,0:13:42.61,Main,Hogback,0,0,0,,As long as she had her beauty...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.80,0:13:46.17,Main,Hogback,0,0,0,,That's Cindry-chan's zombie!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.96,0:13:50.01,Main,Hogback,0,0,0,,I'm full of joy, and so is she.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.42,0:13:54.60,Main,Hogback,0,0,0,,I granted her a second opportunity to live as a human in this world!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.41,0:14:04.82,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,How can you call this human?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.42,0:14:07.65,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,Make her stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.10,0:14:13.54,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,A person with no connection between heart and body can't be called human!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.54,0:14:16.08,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,If you're using soulless bodies...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.08,0:14:19.10,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,you're just creating monsters!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.10,0:14:21.42,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,You make people unhappy by creating those zombies!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.08,0:14:25.80,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,Now that I'm aware of this, I won't let you off!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.80,0:14:30.60,Main,Hogback,0,0,0,,Don't talk to me about "life" with your limited medical skills, pirate-deer!{edited to sound more like an insult - Sky}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.60,0:14:33.31,Main,Hogback,0,0,0,,Cindry-chan, get rid of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.93,0:14:38.89,Main,Hogback,0,0,0,,I'll turn you both into marionettes!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.47,0:14:41.60,Main,Hogback,0,0,0,,You should be grateful, Dr. Chopper.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.60,0:14:47.57,Main,Hogback,0,0,0,,When you die, you'll become\Nthe assistant of the person you admired!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.80,0:14:49.45,Main,Cindry,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Angular Edge Plate...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.85,0:14:53.51,Main,Cindry,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}One!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.95,0:14:54.45,Main,Cindry,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Two!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.53,0:14:55.07,Main,Cindry,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Three!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.83,0:14:59.37,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,Stop...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.03,0:15:00.62,Main,Cindry,0,0,0,,Bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.40,0:15:05.13,Main,Robin,0,0,0,,Chopper!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.96,0:15:13.38,Main,Hogback,0,0,0,,Don't look down on her just because she's a woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.38,0:15:16.60,Main,Hogback,0,0,0,,I've increased her strength for battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.60,0:15:19.75,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,You don't have to listen to him!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.14,0:15:22.90,Main,Cindry,0,0,0,,I will kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.99,0:15:30.52,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,I feel bad for you. You're already dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.52,0:15:33.43,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,How would the rest of your family feel if they knew about this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.89,0:15:35.87,Main,Cindry,0,0,0,,Let me... go!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.87,0:15:40.34,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,Covered with patches, becoming just a mindless soldier...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.34,0:15:41.62,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,Your relatives wouldn't bear to see you like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.62,0:15:43.38,Main,Cindry,0,0,0,,You damned... let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.02,0:15:48.55,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,The heart you were born with is dead now...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.55,0:15:51.77,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,Your body moves under other people's wills...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.77,0:15:53.18,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,What kind of life is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.63,0:15:55.44,Main,Hogback,0,0,0,,You doubt your eyes?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.44,0:16:00.06,Main,Hogback,0,0,0,,Accept it! This is the eternal dream of humans, revival of the dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.06,0:16:01.90,Main,Hogback,0,0,0,,The dead have been resurrected!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.90,0:16:04.06,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,So if they can move, it's enough?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.06,0:16:07.84,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,Humans have more freedom than that!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.84,0:16:12.08,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,You are not even treating them as humans!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.95,0:16:16.87,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,Robin! Hurry and give her salt!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.81,0:16:21.45,Main,Hogback,0,0,0,,Dog-pen!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.45,0:16:22.24,Main,Hogback,0,0,0,,Jigoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.24,0:16:23.81,Main,Hogback,0,0,0,,Help Cindry!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.81,0:16:25.81,Main,Hogback,0,0,0,,Get rid of that nuisance!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.88,0:16:30.96,Main,Robin,0,0,0,,I failed!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.96,0:16:31.90,Main,Robin,0,0,0,,Chopper!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.39,0:16:33.82,Main,Jigoro,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Three Swords Style...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.83,0:16:36.42,Main,Jigoro,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}One-hundred and Eight...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.44,0:16:40.65,Main,Jigoro,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Pound Cannon!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.13,0:16:44.35,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,Stop it, Zoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.04,0:16:46.35,Main,Robin,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Doce Fleur!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.04,0:16:46.35,Note,Robin,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Twelve Flowers
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.98,0:16:52.40,Main,Jigoro,0,0,0,,You nuisance...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.40,0:16:53.35,Main,Jigoro,0,0,0,,Disappear!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.43,0:17:00.87,Main,Dog-Penguin,0,0,0,,Why'd you attack me too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.54,0:17:04.62,Main,Dog-Penguin,0,0,0,,Don't get in my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.65,0:17:09.46,Main,Jigoro,0,0,0,,Now you made me angry!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.46,0:17:10.59,Main,Dog-Penguin,0,0,0,,That'd be you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.59,0:17:12.21,Main,Dog-Penguin,0,0,0,,I received that order!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.88,0:17:15.38,Main,Jigoro,0,0,0,,It was me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.17,0:17:19.60,Main,Hogback,0,0,0,,Hey, what're you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.42,0:17:22.18,Main,Hogback,0,0,0,,Cut it out already!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.18,0:17:23.27,Main,Hogback,0,0,0,,You should be coopera-
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.27,0:17:24.17,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.57,0:17:27.40,Main,Robin,0,0,0,,Such an amusing incident, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.40,0:17:31.40,Main,Robin,0,0,0,,All because of the order given to get rid of the nuisances.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.20,0:17:33.89,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,Even with their memories erased...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.89,0:17:37.70,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,It seems that the true nature of those two is to always be in conflict.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.70,0:17:38.97,Main,Robin,0,0,0,,I'm shocked...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.77,0:17:43.74,Main,Robin,0,0,0,,This seems like a tall tower.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.78,0:17:49.00,Main,Robin,0,0,0,,Why don't you try telling us to jump off it?{Off of here? Remove 'from here'?}{The tower is mentioned in the last line, so "it" is fine - Sky}{dat grammar}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.00,0:17:51.34,Main,Hogback,0,0,0,,What're you implying?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.81,0:17:54.42,Main,Hogback,0,0,0,,That's exactly what I'll say!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.59,0:17:56.59,Main,Hogback,0,0,0,,Jump! Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.59,0:17:59.97,Main,Hogback,0,0,0,,You two there, jump off!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.00,0:18:03.01,Main,Both,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.30,0:18:06.06,Main,Hogback,0,0,0,,N-No, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.06,0:18:18.76,Main,Robin,0,0,0,,We'd rather not.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.51,0:18:23.79,Main,Hogback,0,0,0,,This is unforgivable!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.79,0:18:24.93,Main,Hogback,0,0,0,,You tricked me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.93,0:18:25.90,Main,Hogback,0,0,0,,You're the lowest!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.90,0:18:28.41,Main,Hogback,0,0,0,,You're not human!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.41,0:18:33.09,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,All the zombies will be purified once Luffy takes out Moriah...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.09,0:18:36.45,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,I just want to pummel you, Hogback!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.45,0:18:37.26,Main,Hogback,0,0,0,,Cindry!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.26,0:18:38.75,Main,Hogback,0,0,0,,Buy me some time!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.75,0:18:40.43,Main,Hogback,0,0,0,,I'm getting out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.05,0:18:42.32,Main,Hogback,0,0,0,,Why don't you answer?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.32,0:18:44.26,Main,Hogback,0,0,0,,If you lose, I'll just give you another shadow!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.26,0:18:45.90,Main,Hogback,0,0,0,,Don't worry about dying!{Reworded - Sky}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.67,0:18:50.88,Main,Cindry,0,0,0,,My body...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.17,0:18:53.40,Main,Cindry,0,0,0,,won't move.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.13,0:18:55.78,Main,Hogback,0,0,0,,C-Cindry!
